    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnationis
                        eius millesimo centesimo trigesimo secundo, quarto nonas iulii, indictione
                        nona. Sancta autem et venerabilis <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">ospitali</rs> deo et <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">beati Sancti
                            Gilii</orgName> de loco qui vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                            key="#Churches #Hospitals">Altepascio</placeName>. (…) <persName><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Enrigus</name></persName> filius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wazo">Guazori</name></persName> per hanc
                        cartulam offertionis pro anime mee remedio (…) <ref>dona</ref> iam dicte
                        ecclesie et ospitali (…) integram meam portionem de uno modioro de terra
                        illa que est posita in loco qui vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3209"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Countess"
                            >Ischieto</placeName> et dicitur Aiale, que est recta et detenta per
                        filiis <persName><name ref="Paganus">Paganelli</name></persName> de loco qui
                        vocatur <placeName ref="#places/23">Catiana</placeName> et per filiis
                                <persName><name ref="Binellus">Binelli</name></persName> et per
                        filiis <persName><name ref="Marcus Cacciabectus">Marchi
                            Cacciabecti</name></persName> et per filiis <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus Martinus">Petri Martini</name></persName> et per
                        filiabus <persName><name ref="Burnectus Tuotus">Burnecti
                            Tuoti</name></persName> et per filiabus <persName><name
                                ref="Lambertus Tuotus">Lamberti Tuoti</name></persName>. Competit
                        exinde mihi tres portiones, <rs key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property"
                            >quartam vero portionem</rs> est pertinentes (sic) <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitisse</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3209" key="#Countess">Cicilie</persName>. <ref>Pena
                            in duplum. Maledizioni.</ref> Actum in loco qui vocatur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3200">Ficechio.</placeName> Singnum manus suprascripti
                        Enrichi, qui hancartulam (sic) fieri rogavit. Singna manuum <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Wilicius">Guiliccionis</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Rusticus">Rustici</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rogerius">Rugierii</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidonis</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Omicius">Omici</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Buscus">Busci</name></persName> et
                        aliorum plurimum rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Hubertus">Ubertus</name></persName>
                        donni inperatoris <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs> post traditam complevi et
                        dedi.</ab>
                </div>
